994
02:03:49,885 --> 02:03:51,596
It's a long way away.

995
02:03:51,843 --> 02:03:53,631
Let's go to sleep.

996
02:04:11,405 --> 02:04:14,281
[GUNFlRE]

997
02:04:44,106 --> 02:04:45,144
