Point made.

1057
02:08:31,162 --> 02:08:32,746
Your point, their village.

1058
02:08:33,582 --> 02:08:34,707
Kolya!

1059
02:08:41,298 --> 02:08:44,383
What will you do with your wife
and child in Varykino?

1060
02:08:44,634 --> 02:08:46,427
Just live.

1061
