How lovely.

1070
02:10:11,846 --> 02:10:13,806
Oh, how lovely!

1071
02:10:15,725 --> 02:10:19,019
Hello?

1072
02:10:25,068 --> 02:10:28,612
-Alexander Maximovich?
-Yes.

1073
