1093
02:13:08,106 --> 02:13:11,692
...has expropriated my house
in the name of the people.

1094
02:13:12,652 --> 02:13:13,694
Very well.

1095
02:13:14,279 --> 02:13:17,322
I'm one of the people too!

1096
02:13:18,950 --> 02:13:22,244
