1105
02:14:01,784 --> 02:14:03,660
PETYA:
They didn!t lock the cottage.

1106
02:14:14,255 --> 02:14:16,757
Oh, yes, we can manage here.

1107
02:14:20,386 --> 02:14:22,387
The stove works.

