Lunch.

1194
02:28:25,105 --> 02:28:26,355
Good.

1195
02:28:26,857 --> 02:28:28,649
Come oni you.

1196
02:28:59,681 --> 02:29:00,807
Smell.

1197
02:29:02,643 --> 02:29:03,684
What?

