02:29:05,979 --> 02:29:08,064
This one's a prizefighter.

1199
02:29:08,565 --> 02:29:09,607
Yuri.

1200
02:29:11,902 --> 02:29:13,277
Wait a minute.

1201
02:29:14,279 --> 02:29:15,321
There.

