1203
02:29:37,636 --> 02:29:40,847
Yesi l want to get some morphinei
disinfectant.

1204
02:29:41,098 --> 02:29:43,850
-l shan't need morphine.
-You never know.

1205
02:29:44,101 --> 02:29:45,601
